title: pkgdown template and utilities for rOpenSci docs
text: rotemplate provides custom pkgdown template rOpenSci packages. use render sites https://docs.ropensci.org. Please don’t use package ’s rOpenSci package (.e. use packages listed https://ropensci.org/packages/). Inspired tidytemplate lockedatapkg.
